    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to show you this total beauty. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014it\u2019s basically flawless and drives like a dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new without that dealership price tag, you\u2019ve found it. Come see it for yourself, you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 43500.0,
