    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-grade E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit exhibits flawless mechanical harmony, with the individual throttle bodies providing crisp, linear induction and the Getrag six-speed manual offering short, notch-perfect throws. The VANOS system has been meticulously calibrated to ensure optimal variable valve timing across the entire 8,000 RPM powerband. Structurally, the chassis is impeccable; the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced, while the factory-spec limited-slip differential provides surgical power delivery. Every bushing is pliable, and the underbody remains free of any oxidation or fluid weepage. Finished in a stunning factory coat with zero clear-coat failure, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning enthusiast seeking a benchmark-performance icon with zero deferred maintenance.",
